{"id":144458,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：英国外交部回应议员批评/","date":"2011-04-13T20:30:58Z","modified":"2011-04-13T20:30:58Z","title":"简讯：英国外交部回应议员批评","content":"<div>\n<p>英国外交部对议会批评政府削减BBC国际台经费做出回应。</p>\n<p>外交部说，所有公营部门都必须削减开支。</p>\n<p>早些时候，议会外交委员会批评当局缩减BBC台经费。</p>\n<p>该委员会指出，BBC国际台在提高英国国际形象方面的价值远远超过其成本。</p>\n<p>根据原计划，BBC国际台的经费来源将由英国外交部改为电视执照费，但是议员们质疑这一改变可以令国际台前途更为稳定的说法。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/uk/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/eAy5m91lzMsCDMO_voD6CmCFhew/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/eAy5m91lzMsCDMO_voD6CmCFhew/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/eAy5m91lzMsCDMO_voD6CmCFhew/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/eAy5m91lzMsCDMO_voD6CmCFhew/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/sI8a1Swq4sw\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？请电邮订阅数字时代 <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe me!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}